\pard\qc\b\fs36 MattrMindrScribe Transcript Viewer\line Comprehensive Lag Analysis\b0\fs24\par
\pard\qc\fs20\cf5 Prepared: March 18, 2026 \u8212? Updated: March 18, 2026\line Covers: Frontend, Backend, Database, Infrastructure, Browser, and Safari-Specific Issues\line\line\cf6\b KEY FINDING: Lag is significantly worse in Safari vs Chrome.\line Safari\rquote s rendering engine (WebKit) is the primary amplifier of all issues listed below.\b0\cf0\fs24\par
\pard\par

